#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.round.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.round"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.round.round:1 of
msgid "Round a DataFrame to a variable number of decimal places."
msgstr "将 DataFrame 四舍五入到可变的小数位数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.round.round of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.round.round:3 of
msgid ""
"Number of decimal places to round each column to. If an int is given, "
"round each column to the same number of places. Otherwise dict and Series"
" round to variable numbers of places. Column names should be in the keys "
"if `decimals` is a dict-like. Any columns not included in `decimals` will"
" be left as is. Elements of `decimals` which are not columns of the input"
" will be ignored."
msgstr ""
"每个列要四舍五入到的小数位数。如果给定的是一个整数，则每个列都四舍五入到"
"相同的小数位数。否则，字典和 Series 可以指定不同的小数位数。如果 `"
"decimals` 是类似字典的结构，那么键应为列名。任何不在 `decimals` 中的列将"
"保持不变。不在输入 DataFrame 列中的 `decimals` 元素将被忽略。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.round.round:11
#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.round.round:13 of
msgid ""
"Additional keywords have no effect but might be accepted for "
"compatibility with numpy."
msgstr "额外的关键字没有效果，但为了与 numpy 兼容可能会被接受。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.round.round of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.round.round:16 of
msgid ""
"A DataFrame with the affected columns rounded to the specified number of "
"decimal places."
msgstr "一个 DataFrame，其中受影响的列已四舍五入到指定的小数位数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.round.round of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.round.round:22 of
msgid ":py:obj:`numpy.around`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.round.round:23 of
msgid "Round a numpy array to the given number of decimals."
msgstr "将 numpy 数组四舍五入到给定的小数位数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.round.round:25 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.round`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.round.round:26 of
msgid "Round a Series to the given number of decimals."
msgstr "将 Series 四舍五入到给定的小数位数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.round.round:29 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.round.round:40 of
msgid ""
"By providing an integer each column is rounded to the same number of "
"decimal places"
msgstr "通过提供一个整数，每个列都会四舍五入到相同的小数位数"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.round.round:50 of
msgid ""
"With a dict, the number of places for specific columns can be specified "
"with the column names as key and the number of decimal places as value"
msgstr "通过提供一个字典，可以为特定列指定小数位数，其中键是列名，值是小数位数"

